<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFNohlHenryk_Pl.C3.B6tz">Nohl, Karsten; Henryk Plötz. <a href="http://events.ccc.de/congress/2007/Fahrplan/events/2378.en.html" class="external text" title="http://events.ccc.de/congress/2007/Fahrplan/events/2378.en.html" rel="nofollow">"Mifare: Little Security, Despite Obscurity"</a>. Chaos Communication Congress<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://events.ccc.de/congress/2007/Fahrplan/events/2378.en.html" class="external free" title="http://events.ccc.de/congress/2007/Fahrplan/events/2378.en.html" rel="nofollow">http://events.ccc.de/congress/2007/Fahrplan/events/2378.en.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Mifare%3A+Little+Security%2C+Despite+Obscurity&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Nohl&amp;rft.aufirst=Karsten&amp;rft.au=Nohl%2C+Karsten&amp;rft.au=Henryk+Pl%C3%B6tz&amp;rft.pub=Chaos+Communication+Congress&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fevents.ccc.de%2Fcongress%2F2007%2FFahrplan%2Fevents%2F2378.en.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:MIFARE"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFNohl2007">Nohl, Karsten (2007-12-28). <a href="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=4252367680974396650&amp;hl=en" class="external text" title="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=4252367680974396650&amp;hl=en" rel="nofollow">"24C3 - Mifare security - #2378"</a>. Chaos Communication Congress<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=4252367680974396650&amp;hl=en" class="external free" title="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=4252367680974396650&amp;hl=en" rel="nofollow">http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=4252367680974396650&amp;hl=en</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=24C3+-+Mifare+security+-+%232378&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Nohl&amp;rft.aufirst=Karsten&amp;rft.au=Nohl%2C+Karsten&amp;rft.date=2007-12-28&amp;rft.pub=Chaos+Communication+Congress&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.google.com%2Fvideoplay%3Fdocid%3D4252367680974396650%26hl%3Den&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:MIFARE"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFNohlDavid_Evans2008">Nohl, Karsten; David Evans (2008-08-01). "<a href="http://www.usenix.org/events/sec08/tech/nohl.html" class="external text" title="http://www.usenix.org/events/sec08/tech/nohl.html" rel="nofollow">Reverse-Engineering a Cryptographic RFID Tag</a>". <i>Proceedings of the 17th USENIX Security Symposium</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.usenix.org/events/sec08/tech/nohl.html" class="external free" title="http://www.usenix.org/events/sec08/tech/nohl.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.usenix.org/events/sec08/tech/nohl.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Reverse-Engineering+a+Cryptographic+RFID+Tag&amp;rft.jtitle=Proceedings+of+the+17th+USENIX+Security+Symposium&amp;rft.aulast=Nohl&amp;rft.aufirst=Karsten&amp;rft.au=Nohl%2C+Karsten&amp;rft.au=David+Evans&amp;rft.date=2008-08-01&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.usenix.org%2Fevents%2Fsec08%2Ftech%2Fnohl.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:MIFARE"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
